    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Plates or overlapping pieces of metal worn on military uniforms at the shoulder to indicate rank or unit; worn especially during the 19th century.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
